00:29:33,810 --> 00:29:35,010
It could be

567
00:29:35,010 --> 00:29:37,250
simply wonderful moments
that didn't end well.

568
00:29:37,330 --> 00:29:38,890
Look at you.

569
00:29:38,890 --> 00:29:40,250
Despising me for falling in love.

570
00:29:40,250 --> 00:29:41,850
Annoying.

571
00:29:42,640 --> 00:29:44,400
Same to you,

572
00:29:44,400 --> 00:29:45,530
you highly

573
00:29:45,530 --> 00:29:47,040
ignorant guy.

574
00:29:51,000 --> 00:29:53,640
What have Chu Li done wrong?

575
00:29:59,730 --> 00:30:01,210
Ah Xiang.

576
00:30:01,210 --> 00:30:03,930
If... I mean, if.

577
00:30:03,930 --> 00:30:06,170
If you found out that the person you like

578
00:30:06,170 --> 00:30:08,490
is actually your
long time internet friend,

579
00:30:08,490 --> 00:30:10,850
who has been keeping the truth from you

580
00:30:10,850 --> 00:30:12,330
even after learning it

581
00:30:12,330 --> 00:30:13,290
a long time ago,

582
00:30:13,290 --> 00:30:15,690
and he created two accounts to fool you,

583
00:30:15,690 --> 00:30:17,770
not planning

584
00:30:17,770 --> 00:30:19,210
to tell you the truth.

585
00:30:19,210 --> 00:30:20,720
What would you do then?

586
00:30:22,210 --> 00:30:26,330
Is it about your friend?

587
00:30:30,530 --> 00:30:31,570
Chu Li.

588
00:30:31,570 --> 00:30:34,330
I think that guy has gone too far.

589
00:30:34,330 --> 00:30:35,210
Right?

590
00:30:35,210 --> 00:30:37,370
This is irritating,

591
00:30:37,370 --> 00:30:38,730
isn't it?

592
00:30:38,970 --> 00:30:41,050
That was my first ever Valentine's Day.

593
00:30:41,050 --> 00:30:43,010
Not only did I receive any present,

594
00:30:43,010 --> 00:30:45,570
I even found out that he is a liar.

595
00:30:45,570 --> 00:30:47,810
This is too much for me to take.

596
00:30:51,130 --> 00:30:53,450
You finally admit

597
00:30:53,450 --> 00:30:56,530
that you are the friend.

598
00:31:00,130 --> 00:31:03,890
Did you realise that long ago?

599
00:31:05,050 --> 00:31:08,770
Well, not exposing someone is a virtue.

600
00:31:08,770 --> 00:31:11,090
You won't be mad at me, will you?

601
00:31:11,090 --> 00:31:12,210
Of course not.

602
00:31:12,210 --> 00:31:15,090
You kept quiet
so that I won't feel awkward.

603
00:31:15,090 --> 00:31:17,450
It's different from that heartless guy.

604
00:31:18,450 --> 00:31:20,090
Don't be mad, Chu Li.

605
00:31:20,090 --> 00:31:22,090
Ignore him.

606
00:31:22,090 --> 00:31:23,410
Let's go home.

607
00:31:23,880 --> 00:31:25,450
Exactly what I thought.

608
00:32:36,770 --> 00:32:38,410
Where is she?

609
00:32:39,450 --> 00:32:41,290
Why isn't she home yet?

610
00:32:49,090 --> 00:32:51,050
How come her luggage isn't here?

611
00:33:00,890 --> 00:33:02,330
[Where are you?]

612
00:33:03,060 --> 00:33:08,470
[Zhou Chuan]

613
00:33:08,510 --> 00:33:33,550
[Little Monkey]

614
00:33:08,810 --> 00:33:09,840
[Ah Xiang's place.]

615
00:33:09,840 --> 00:33:10,890
[I'm staying here for now.]

616
00:33:10,890 --> 00:33:12,650
[You won't even feed Er Gou?]

617
00:33:12,650 --> 00:33:14,930
[What does your
conscience say about that?]

618
00:33:14,930 --> 00:33:17,410
[Running away from home just like that.]

619
00:33:17,410 --> 00:33:18,290
[Aren't you incredible?]

620
00:33:18,290 --> 00:33:20,050
[So you're rich now?]

621
00:33:32,570 --> 00:33:34,130
Okay.

622
00:33:33,550 --> 00:33:34,300
[Zhou Chuan]

623
00:33:45,380 --> 00:33:47,720
[Not Drama King, it's Saviour: Okay]

624
00:33:56,890 --> 00:33:58,650
What... What's wrong?

625
00:33:58,650 --> 00:34:01,250
Did that guy say something?

626
00:34:01,250 --> 00:34:03,320
Nothing. Don't bring him up.

627
00:34:03,320 --> 00:34:04,200
I plan

628
00:34:04,200 --> 00:34:06,970
to buy a cheap spring bed

629
00:34:06,970 --> 00:34:08,130
and stay longer here.

630
00:34:08,130 --> 00:34:08,810
Is that okay?

631
00:34:08,810 --> 00:34:09,850
Sure.

632
00:34:09,850 --> 00:34:11,850
Stay as long as you like.

633
00:34:20,450 --> 00:34:21,610
This is really tasty.

634
00:34:21,610 --> 00:34:24,000
I want to buy ten more.

635
00:34:24,170 --> 00:34:25,490
Which flavour would you like?

636
00:34:25,490 --> 00:34:28,490
I love the braised meat one.

637
00:34:55,010 --> 00:34:56,089
Someone

638
00:34:56,649 --> 00:34:57,850
irresponsibly broke

639
00:34:57,850 --> 00:34:58,770
my 28-year-long

640
00:34:58,770 --> 00:35:00,730
unrestrained lifestyle,

641
00:35:00,730 --> 00:35:01,960
and made me getting used to

642
00:35:01,960 --> 00:35:03,720
eating on proper time.

643
00:35:03,720 --> 00:35:05,010
But now?

644
00:35:05,890 --> 00:35:08,370
All of a sudden,
I no longer have meals ready on time.

645
00:35:09,330 --> 00:35:10,609
Wouldn't you

646
00:35:10,609 --> 00:35:12,169
feel upset?

647
00:35:16,250 --> 00:35:18,770
You at least have your canned food.

648
00:35:19,330 --> 00:35:20,530
But me?

649
00:35:21,410 --> 00:35:23,250
I have nothing to eat.

650
00:35:24,510 --> 00:35:33,360
[Zhou Chuan: Where are you? Little Monkey:
Ah Xiang's place for now. Zhou Chuan: Okay.]

651
00:35:29,490 --> 00:35:31,330
It's been a week.

652
00:35:31,330 --> 00:35:33,210
She doesn't even bother to
urge me to deliver my work.

653
00:35:38,690 --> 00:35:40,730
Is she really not coming back?

654
00:35:47,450 --> 00:35:48,770
Who's that?

655
00:35:51,410 --> 00:35:52,360
Hi.

656
00:35:52,360 --> 00:35:54,330
I'm here to clean the house.

657
00:35:55,850 --> 00:35:57,450
Did you make a mistake?

658
00:35:57,450 --> 00:35:58,570
Excuse me.

659
00:35:58,960 --> 00:35:59,930
Hello, Jiang Yu Cheng.

660
00:35:59,930 --> 00:36:00,810
Hello.

661
00:36:01,600 --> 00:36:02,770
Chu Li isn't home.

662
00:36:02,770 --> 00:36:05,120
Isn't it time to clean your house?

663
00:36:05,120 --> 00:36:06,440
I ordered a cleaner for you.

664
00:36:07,130 --> 00:36:09,010
She should have arrived.

665
00:36:09,490 --> 00:36:11,490
Mind your own business.

666
00:36:12,210 --> 00:36:13,610
Thanks.

667
00:36:20,570 --> 00:36:20,970
Hi.

668
00:36:20,970 --> 00:36:23,450
I'm a cleaner.

669
00:36:23,450 --> 00:36:26,170
Did you order a three-hour
cleaning service?

670
00:36:26,360 --> 00:36:28,010
Where should I work on?

671
00:36:28,410 --> 00:36:29,490
Come on in.

672
00:36:29,490 --> 00:36:30,530
Okay.

673
00:36:31,930 --> 00:36:33,210
So,

674
00:36:34,330 --> 00:36:36,730
do as you see fit.

675
00:36:36,970 --> 00:36:38,090
Okay.

676
00:36:42,890 --> 00:36:44,730
No, Jiang Yu Cheng.

677
00:36:45,410 --> 00:36:47,650
How do you know Chu Li isn't at my house?

678
00:36:47,810 --> 00:36:50,730
I even know
she's staying at Ah Xiang's place.

679
00:36:51,880 --> 00:36:53,640
How could you only reply an "okay"?

680
00:36:53,640 --> 00:36:55,490
I'm speechless.

681
00:36:55,490 --> 00:36:56,970
I spent hours

682
00:36:56,970 --> 00:36:59,040
explaining to you the mindset of a woman.

683
00:36:59,040 --> 00:37:00,570
Did you keep it in mind?

684
00:37:00,570 --> 00:37:01,930
Hold on.

685
00:37:02,490 --> 00:37:03,530
You haven't told me

686
00:37:03,530 --> 00:37:05,530
how did you know Chu Li isn't at my house?

687
00:37:06,690 --> 00:37:08,160
Are you two together?

688
00:37:08,450 --> 00:37:10,850
We're checking on the
book cover at the printing factory.

689
00:37:11,690 --> 00:37:12,770
[I'll try to get you]

690
00:37:12,770 --> 00:37:13,930
[Ah Xiang's address.]

691
00:37:13,930 --> 00:37:15,410
[Don't let the chance slip.]

692
00:37:15,410 --> 00:37:17,330
Remember, no matter what,

693
00:37:17,330 --> 00:37:19,090
apologise first.

694
00:37:19,090 --> 00:37:20,370
Oka...

695
00:37:21,730 --> 00:37:23,410
Stop nagging. I'm hanging up. Bye.

696
00:37:35,560 --> 00:37:37,320
I can drive you home.

697
00:37:37,320 --> 00:37:38,530
Never mind.

698
00:37:38,530 --> 00:37:40,770
Ah Xiang's place is just
two train stations away.

699
00:37:40,770 --> 00:37:41,730
It's convenient.

700
00:37:41,730 --> 00:37:43,090
No problem.

701
00:37:43,090 --> 00:37:44,040
Since it's near,

702
00:37:44,040 --> 00:37:45,800
I can get you home very quickly.

703
00:37:46,120 --> 00:37:48,810
Then, thanks, Mr Jiang.

704
00:37:49,760 --> 00:37:51,330
I should be thanking you.

705
00:37:51,610 --> 00:37:52,650
It's been a while

706
00:37:52,650 --> 00:37:54,130
since I saw my own new book cover

707
00:37:54,410 --> 00:37:55,650
that I thought I won't

708
00:37:55,650 --> 00:37:57,130
get to publish books anymore.

709
00:37:57,610 --> 00:37:59,290
Don't say that.

710
00:37:59,530 --> 00:38:00,930
Being able to

711
00:38:00,930 --> 00:38:02,080
publish your book

712
00:38:02,080 --> 00:38:04,450
still seems unrealistic to me even today.

713
00:38:04,450 --> 00:38:05,850
When I saw the book cover,

714
00:38:05,850 --> 00:38:08,250
I got so emotional that
I couldn't sleep for nights.

715
00:38:08,250 --> 00:38:10,050
I guess when I see the real book,

716
00:38:10,050 --> 00:38:12,810
I will cry out of excitement.

717
00:38:13,050 --> 00:38:16,010
But I think there's another reason

718
00:38:16,010 --> 00:38:17,850
why you couldn't sleep.

719
00:38:19,290 --> 00:38:22,930
No, there isn't.

720
00:38:24,080 --> 00:38:24,970
Let's go.

721
00:38:24,970 --> 00:38:26,690
Give me Ah Xiang's address.

722
00:38:35,130 --> 00:38:36,530
Come on, Er Gou.

723
00:38:52,410 --> 00:38:54,010
Go, Er Gou.

724
00:38:57,530 --> 00:39:00,250
Why are you here, Er Gou?

725
00:39:02,890 --> 00:39:04,650
What a coincidence.

726
00:39:05,800 --> 00:39:07,450
You talk. I'll get going.

727
00:39:07,450 --> 00:39:09,050
Thank you, Mr Jiang.

728
00:39:12,530 --> 00:39:14,090
Why are you here?

729
00:39:17,170 --> 00:39:18,880
I'm walking my dog.

730
00:39:20,170 --> 00:39:21,730
You sure have been walking far.

731
00:39:21,730 --> 00:39:24,210
Carry on. I'm leaving.

732
00:39:25,210 --> 00:39:27,010
Do you really hate to see me that much?

733
00:39:27,010 --> 00:39:28,650
Why do you pull a long
face when you see me,

734
00:39:28,650 --> 00:39:30,410
and keep smiling when
you see Jiang Yu Cheng?

735
00:39:30,410 --> 00:39:32,170
He doesn't lie to me.

736
00:39:32,170 --> 00:39:34,210
Nor did he fool me
with different accounts.

737
00:39:34,210 --> 00:39:36,330
And he didn't live in a house with you,

738
00:39:36,330 --> 00:39:38,290
or cook and walk the dog with you.

739
00:39:39,130 --> 00:39:40,610
Fine. I don't want to talk to you.

740
00:39:40,610 --> 00:39:41,610
What do you mean by "fine"?

741
00:39:41,880 --> 00:39:43,320
Like, let's break up?

742
00:39:44,970 --> 00:39:46,840
What am I to you?

743
00:39:51,090 --> 00:39:52,090
A writer.

744
00:39:52,170 --> 00:39:53,440
An internet friend.

745
00:39:53,610 --> 00:39:54,970
A boyfriend.

746
00:39:54,970 --> 00:39:56,250
Or neighbour?

747
00:39:57,400 --> 00:39:59,330
I don't even know.

748
00:40:00,970 --> 00:40:02,770
Let me ask you.

749
00:40:02,770 --> 00:40:04,530
If I hadn't found it out,

750
00:40:04,530 --> 00:40:06,690
when would you tell me the truth?

751
00:40:07,050 --> 00:40:07,890
Must you

752
00:40:07,890 --> 00:40:08,960
know everything

753
00:40:08,960 --> 00:40:10,370
about your internet friend?

754
00:40:11,570 --> 00:40:13,690
So you don't think you did anything wrong.

755
00:40:13,690 --> 00:40:15,330
What's the point of coming to see me?

756
00:40:15,330 --> 00:40:16,650
I'm just taking Er Gou here to ask

757
00:40:16,650 --> 00:40:18,290
when will you come home?

758
00:40:18,850 --> 00:40:20,330
You've stayed too long here.

759
00:40:20,330 --> 00:40:21,770
It's time to come home.

760
00:40:23,360 --> 00:40:24,850
Er Gou and I have lost weight.

761
00:40:26,850 --> 00:40:27,970
It's not my business.

762
00:40:27,970 --> 00:40:29,490
I'm not your maid.

763
00:40:29,490 --> 00:40:30,770
Chu Li.

764
00:40:30,770 --> 00:40:32,650
You're back from the printing factory?

765
00:40:32,650 --> 00:40:34,090
Hi, Mr Zhou Chuan.

766
00:40:34,530 --> 00:40:36,330
Er Gou is here too?

767
00:40:39,090 --> 00:40:40,930
I...

768
00:40:40,930 --> 00:40:43,690
Did I disturb you?

769
00:40:43,690 --> 00:40:45,810
No, we're done.

770
00:40:45,810 --> 00:40:47,770
Mr Zhou Chuan was going to leave.

771
00:40:47,770 --> 00:40:48,730
Yes.

772
00:40:49,410 --> 00:40:51,410
I can't deliver my new
outline on time anyway.

773
00:40:51,410 --> 00:40:53,960
I'm just telling you. Bye.

774
00:40:54,330 --> 00:40:56,210
-Let's go.
-Bye, Mr Zhou Chuan.

775
00:41:07,210 --> 00:41:08,650
You saw that, didn't you?

776
00:41:08,650 --> 00:41:11,290
She wanted to draw the line with me.

777
00:41:11,770 --> 00:41:13,570
It's only been one week.

778
00:41:13,570 --> 00:41:15,200
Where has her manners gone?

779
00:41:16,250 --> 00:41:17,090
I should've recorded that

780
00:41:17,090 --> 00:41:18,450
and show it to her.

781
00:41:18,850 --> 00:41:20,360
That is too much.

782
00:41:22,370 --> 00:41:23,330
Also...

783
00:41:24,610 --> 00:41:26,050
Look at me.

784
00:41:26,810 --> 00:41:28,530
What's the use of a leash?

785
00:41:29,050 --> 00:41:30,650
Why didn't you hold me back?

786
00:41:31,040 --> 00:41:32,330
I've actually decided to...

787
00:41:35,050 --> 00:41:37,490
I've already decided to apologise first.

788
00:41:53,410 --> 00:41:55,210
Is that your sister?

789
00:41:59,320 --> 00:42:00,810
It's you?

790
00:42:02,010 --> 00:42:03,090
Where's Chu Li?

791
00:42:15,330 --> 00:42:16,570
You screwed up?

792
00:42:18,560 --> 00:42:19,290
Didn't I say

793
00:42:19,290 --> 00:42:20,850
to apologise first?

794
00:42:20,850 --> 00:42:22,490
Swallow your pride.

795
00:42:22,490 --> 00:42:23,490
Why won't you learn?

796
00:42:23,490 --> 00:42:25,170
You're one to talk.

797
00:42:25,690 --> 00:42:27,770
Why does she always smile
so happily when she sees you,

798
00:42:27,770 --> 00:42:29,610
and pull a long face when she sees me?

799
00:42:30,120 --> 00:42:31,930
When I think about it,

800
00:42:32,490 --> 00:42:34,770
I can't help but get mad.

801
00:42:36,490 --> 00:42:37,530
Hey.

802
00:42:37,530 --> 00:42:39,130
What a jealous guy.

803
00:42:39,130 --> 00:42:40,250
Seriously.

804
00:42:40,250 --> 00:42:42,090
Can't you stop being jealous?

805
00:42:48,650 --> 00:42:50,040
Listen.

806
00:42:50,610 --> 00:42:51,610
I

807
00:42:51,610 --> 00:42:53,250
am the writer Chu Li is working with.

808
00:42:53,250 --> 00:42:55,320
Of course she will be polite to me.

809
00:42:55,320 --> 00:42:57,050
Why would she treat you the same way?

810
00:42:57,200 --> 00:42:58,210
If she does,

811
00:42:58,210 --> 00:42:59,400
then you should really be mad.

812
00:42:59,400 --> 00:43:00,720
Think about that.

813
00:43:00,720 --> 00:43:02,330
What should I do now?

814
00:43:04,610 --> 00:43:06,610
I actually planned to have a meal here

815
00:43:06,610 --> 00:43:08,250
if Chu Li is in.

816
00:43:08,250 --> 00:43:09,730
Seems like I'd better leave.

817
00:43:09,840 --> 00:43:12,530
I'll place a delivery order.

818
00:43:14,410 --> 00:43:16,210
Pick what you want.

819
00:43:17,610 --> 00:43:18,640
Such kindness.

820
00:43:18,640 --> 00:43:19,850
What do you want?

821
00:43:20,840 --> 00:43:23,890
Update me on what Chu Li is doing anytime.

822
00:43:24,650 --> 00:43:27,250
Since she's always nice to you.

823
00:43:28,850 --> 00:43:30,850
I want the most pricey
Buddha's Temptation.

824
00:43:30,850 --> 00:43:33,090
1,988 yuan per portion.

825
00:43:33,330 --> 00:43:34,130
That expensive?

826
00:43:34,130 --> 00:43:35,810
What is added to it?

827
00:43:38,120 --> 00:43:39,970
Just order it.

828
00:43:42,890 --> 00:43:44,330
Two portions?

829
00:43:44,330 --> 00:43:46,370
One, for yourself.

830
00:43:49,450 --> 00:43:50,970
I'm not hungry.
